<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7642> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7642" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Cos. 174. Tr. Mil. 171. In MRR 1.417, refer also to Liv. 42.49.9. On Mucius and P. Cornelius Lentulus (202), see Schleussner, Legaten 104, note 17. On Lentulus as a legate, see also Livy 42.56.4.\n" .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/2664> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #2664" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Sent as a Legatus of Licinius to hold Ambracia (Liv. 42.67.9)." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/2653> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #2653" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Commanded the center at Callinicus (Liv. 42.58.13). See Legates." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/2556> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #2556" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Liv. 43.2.9, cf. 41.21.4; Fast. Cap., Degrassi 48f., 123, 458f.; Plin. NH 2.99; Chr. 354; Cassiod.; and on Scaevola, Fast. Hyd.; Chr. Pasc. On Postumius, see Münzer, APF 213ff." .
